<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If you set a date like this :</p>

<p>$zend_test = new Zend_Date();
$zend_test-&gt;set('2008-12-22', 'YYYY-MM-dd');</p>

<p>var_dump($zend_test-&gt;get(Zend_Date::ISO_8601));</p>

<p>will result in 2008-12-22T00:00:00+01:00</p>

<p>but if you add 7 days or 1 week 
$zend_test-&gt;addWeek(1);
var_dump( $zend_test-&gt;get('YYYY-MM-dd'));
var_dump($zend_test-&gt;get(Zend_Date::ISO_8601));</p>

<p>will result in : 
string(10) "2009-12-29"
string(25) "2008-12-29T00:00:00+01:00"</p>

<p>1 day less ( $zend_test-&gt;addDays(6) ) works perfectly</p>

